data.description: Sweet Neat & Complete single-level living. This residence features a welcoming open floor plan with an eat in kitchen equipped with stainless steel appliances and sturdy wood cabinetry. Enjoy the convenience of a dedicated laundry closet, three generously sized bedrooms, and two full baths. Nestled on a level one-acre lot, surrounded by a fenced-in yard, this property includes a delightful stream at the rear, creating a perfect outdoor space for playtime, gatherings, and gardening. The expansive rear deck provides two designated areas for grilling and chilling. With an attached garage and paved driveway, parking is a breeze. Ideally situated for easy access to amenities and major highways.
